Being an IMG with a medical training background so few applicants undergo and match successfully, made me realize how toxic this world can be. I've received tons of "misinformation", people claiming to know so many things and putting me down and scaring me that with this background, I probably wouldn't be able to match.

In comes Dr. Desai. He helped me get on track, reassured me and dispelled most of the nonsense others were feeding me. With his help, and essentially making his The Successful Residency Match 2017 book my new Bible, I received 18 interview offers, excelled at them, and matched at my 2nd choice institution.

review_text:
This review is based on the billing issues at Pahlavani dental. I received one notification in December 2018 about a bill in need of payment. I was confused, as I had changed jobs and therefore insurance, and hadn't visited Pahlavani dental in several months. I clicked through the email to see what the balance was due, but it showed me nothing. So I went on with my business.

Seven months later, I received a notification from a collections agency that Pahlavani dental sold that bill (which no one was still able to verify for me the amount). I called Pahlavani dental and they could neither confirm the amount nor who the creditor was, since they'd batch sold the debt. They were able to tell me that my insurance had retroactively denied one of their claims, which I was not notified about, and they were billing me for the service. I had to send them the name of the collection agency for them to confirm. I paid the stupid creditor $119 and yet now I have a negative impact on my credit because of Pahlavani's billing practices. I would not recommend dealing with this.

review_text:
Lovely outfits, amazing app, great customer service.
For the quality of the material we should always check in “Details” there’s everything there to choose properly.

I placed 4 orders during the covid because all the shops in my area were closed. My baby was just born and I needed clothes. I waited for the first order very long time, but as soon as I wrote an email they immediately answered me back. With various options to resolve the issue.
When they sent the wrong size they gave me a full refund and they let me to keep the items to use as a gift for friends with that size. This was solved in 2 days Sunday and Monday.

In my opinion very remarkable.
The quality is very nice if you order clothes you should check the quality Of the material in the description. I bought a dress 100% cotton and it respected the expectations.

I’ve ordered the May 25/26 and received June 13. Very improved.

review_text:
(Translated by Google) Very happy with my first order of 5 sets of baby clothes from you that were nicely packaged in nice bags. Ordered for large size deliberately. To be sure they would fit. Several garments were finer than in the pictures. Glad I chose a larger size as clothes that are stated in months / age sizes instead of centimeters differ a lot.
Not happy with the company that delivered the package. Early Bird as they are called. They had put only half of the bag of clothes tucked in the mailbox - despite the fact that there was room to put the bag down completely. It was pouring rain outside. Anyone could have passed by and stolen the bag from the mailbox outside our plot. Would have preferred it to be delivered to the nearest agent where you can pick up your package yourself.

(Original)
Mycket nöjd med min första beställning av  5 set babykläder från er som var fint paketerade i fina påsar. Beställde för stor storlek medvetet. För att vara säker att de skulle passa. Flera plagg var finare än på bilderna. Glad jag valde större storlek då kläder som anges i månader/åldersstorlekar istället för centimeter skiljer sig åt mycket.
Inte nöjd med företaget som levererade paketet. Early Bird som de heter. De hade lagt påsen med kläder endast till hälften nedstoppat i brevlådan - trots det fanns plats att stoppa ner påsen helt. Det ösregnade ute. Vem som  helst hade kunnat gå förbi och stjäla påsen från brevlådan utanför vår tomt.  Hade hellre velat att det levererats till närmaste ombud där man själv kan hämta ut sitt paket.
